A name is a stable identity over time.
A particular has an unstable identity over time.

Causal identity?
Named identity?
Physical identity?

Programming is held back by not understanding the concept of identity.

Wars of functional vs not, mutable vs not center around a misunderstanding of identity of data.

Class identity.

